French: La Bastille est une forteresse historique en France.
English: The Bastille is a historical fortress in France.

French: Le Louvre est un muséum très fameux à Paris.
English: The Louvre is a very famous museum in Paris.

English: The Eiffel Tower was built for the World's Fair in 1889.

French: Le Château de Versailles est un patrimoine culturel majeur de la France.

English: The Saint Chapel is a royal chapel from the 13th century in Paris.
